  <brief_title>Study to Assess the Safety of REGN668 (SAR231893) Administered Concomitantly With Topical Corticosteroids (TCS) in Patients With Moderate-to-severe Atopic Dermatitis (AD)</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Randomized, Double-Blind, Parallel-Group, Placebo-Controlled Study to Assess the Safety of REGN668 Administered Concomitantly With Topical Corticosteroids to Patients With Moderate-to-Severe Atopic Dermatitis</official_title>
