  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the safety of REGN668 (SAR231893) administered
      concomitantly with topical corticosteroids (TCS) in patients with moderate-to-severe atopic
      dermatitis (AD).
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
